snippet.title: RAW DATA | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
RAW DATA Full Release Now Available on HTC Vive and Oculus! 
Coming October 10 to PSVR.

Raw Data on Steam: http://bit.ly/RawDataOnSteam
Raw Data on Oculus http://bit.ly/RawDataOculusLive
Official site: http://www.Survios.com/RawData
Learn more about Eden Corp: http://www.edencorp.tokyo

Built from the ground up for VR, Raw Data’s action gameplay, intuitive controls, challenging enemies, and sci-fi atmosphere will completely immerse you within the surreal world of Eden Corp. Become the adrenaline-charged heroes of your own futuristic technothriller.


Music by:
Jeremy Nathan Tisser 
Pertubator
